      <title>《明报》称香港拒绝法国美联社记者入境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/hong-kong-denies-entry-to-french-journalist</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港拒绝一名试图以游客身份进入香港的法国摄影记者入境，这一事件可能加剧人们对香港新闻自由的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/hong-kong-denies-entry-to-french-journalist</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 10:02:14 GMT</pubDate>
